sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Human
    participant RealApp as Real ChatGPT<br/>(tab in Chrome)
    participant Replicata as replicata core<br/>(Node.js)
    participant Renderer as user's renderer<br/>(localhost:5173)
    participant UI as replicata UI tab
    participant Server as replicata HTTP server

    Note over Human,Server: Installation (on replicata start)
    Replicata->>RealApp: install event-tap<br/>(document-level capture listeners:<br/>click/mousedown/mouseup/focus/blur/<br/>keydown/keyup/input/change/submit)
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataSetTags([...])<br/>(populates browser-side match cache)
    Replicata->>Renderer: install event-fire<br/>(__replicataFireEvent + pair reporter)

    Note over Renderer: Pair reporting (continuous)
    Renderer->>Renderer: MutationObserver on [data-replicata-tag]<br/>(debounced 300ms)
    Renderer-)Replicata: __replicataReportPairs(["send-button", "message-input"])
    Replicata->>Replicata: update rendererPairs Set
    UI->>Server: GET /tags (polling)
    Server-->>UI: tags w/ paired: true | false
    UI->>UI: render ↔ (paired) or "copy attr" (unpaired)

    Note over Human,Server: User event forwarding
    Human->>RealApp: types in tagged textarea
    RealApp->>RealApp: browser fires input event<br/>(target = contenteditable)
    Note over RealApp: event-tap capture-phase handler fires
    RealApp->>RealApp: findMatchingTags(target) —<br/>scans cached Map<tagName, Element[]><br/>checking target === el or el.contains(target)
    RealApp->>RealApp: extractDetail(event) — pulls<br/>{type, button, key, clientX,<br/>ctrlKey, value, ...}<br/>(textContent fallback for contenteditable)
    RealApp-)Replicata: __replicataEvent(tagName, type, detail)<br/>(fire-and-forget, one call per matched tag)

    Replicata->>Renderer: page.evaluate __replicataFireEvent<br/>(tagName, type, detail)
    Renderer->>Renderer: querySelectorAll<br/>([data-replicata-tag="tagName"])
    Renderer->>Renderer: dispatch new MouseEvent /<br/>KeyboardEvent / Event (bubbles: true)
    Renderer->>Renderer: user's onClick / onInput /<br/>onKeyDown handler fires

    Note over RealApp: Cache invalidation
    RealApp->>RealApp: DOM mutates (page content changes)
    RealApp->>RealApp: event-tap MutationObserver<br/>(debounced 500ms)
    RealApp->>RealApp: recomputeCache() —<br/>re-resolves each tag's selectors,<br/>refills Map<tagName, Element[]>

    Note over Replicata,Renderer: Tag set changes (user adds/removes/broadens)
    Replicata->>RealApp: __replicataSetTags(newTagList)
    RealApp->>RealApp: recomputeCache()
